rows.label: tlk45300021_01_msg0001
rows.name:
I moved my family here from
Superbia because I heard it was
a really safe place to live...

rows.label: tlk45300021_01_msg0002
rows.name:
A fight between those Iira terrorists
and Superbia's finest Blade is exactly
NOT what I signed up for!

rows.label: tlk45300021_01_msg0003
rows.name:
I just want my wife and daughter to
have a peaceful life, but at this
rate, it seems this isn't it...

rows.label: tlk45300021_01_msg0004
rows.name:
I hope all this gets sorted out
sooner rather than later. It feels
like the whole city's on edge.
